race.comment: Tricky way to start the Quaddie and we might need a few. REMIGIUS (6) is close to breaking through after two consecutive placings, the latest coming when third over 1600m at Ararat. Should have more improvement to come out of that than FASHION FIGHTER, so can turn the tables. REAL INTRIGUE (3) should have derived benefit from three runs back after a long break and can improve sharply here. BALTIC WAY (1), like REMIGIUS, comes through the FASHION FIGHTER race and will be much better for that. FASHION FIGHTER (4) turned things around big time last start, but want to see him repeat the dose, although he gets the chance to do so from the inside alley.
